# Calculator Website

This project is a simple calculator website that performs basic arithmetic operations.

## Features
- Perform addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division.
- Clean and intuitive interface.


### How to Use
1. Open the calculator in your browser.
2. Enter numbers and choose the operation.
3. See the result displayed instantly.

